# Employee Registration System

A simple Java console application to register employees, verify IDs, and update salaries. (Project made to test what I learned!)

## 📂 Structure

Main.java
└── utilities/
├── CheckId.java
├── RegisterNewEmployee.java
└── ModifySalaries.java

└── registeredEmployees/
└── RegisteredEmployees.java

└── peoples/
└── Employee.java

## ⚙️ Features

- Register employees with unique IDs
- Check if an ID is already used
- Increase salary by percentage
- Organized with static utility classes

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Compile with `javac` or run via IntelliJ
2. Interact via console prompts

## 🛠 Technologies

- Java 17+ (Works with Java 8+, but the project uses modern features)
- IntelliJ IDEA (recomendado)

